00:42:46,965 --> 00:42:50,388
I'm bowing a guitar between C, sorry, C sharp and D,

735
00:42:51,028 --> 00:42:53,110
and I've spread that out across four octaves,

736
00:42:53,170 --> 00:42:54,932
and all I'm doing is just slowly bowing

737
00:42:54,972 --> 00:42:56,653
between those two notes, and I recorded that

738
00:42:56,933 --> 00:42:57,934
a whole bunch of different times

