00:43:00,757 --> 00:43:01,757
It's really, really quite a cool thing.

742
00:43:02,238 --> 00:43:03,999
Again, it's kind of using guitars in an interesting way

743
00:43:04,019 --> 00:43:04,960
to get that horror thing across.

